{"tid":1922944,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿迪達披露感染新冠過程！週二曾帶阿仙奴集訓","createTime":"2020-03-13T00:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T13:22:34.000Z","uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"672c82944307eef8b1c59c1cd0607eb729fd92db","tid":1922944,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T00:09:55.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴主教練阿迪達確定感染新冠病毒，在確診之後，阿迪達談到了自己的檢測過程和看法。<br />\n<br />\n  阿迪達表示：「真的很令人失望，我是在感覺不舒服後接受了檢查。我希望能在條件允許後盡快地返回到崗位上。」<br />\n<br />\n  名記Charles Watt透露，阿迪達本週二帶領阿仙奴進行了訓練，本週三他感覺身體不舒服，隨後接受了核酸檢測。由此來看，阿仙奴球員隔離的時間應該是從本週二算起。<br />\n<br />\n  該記者還表示，阿迪達並沒和此前確診感染新冠病毒的奧林比亞高斯老闆有接觸。所以阿迪達是如何感染病毒的，如今依然還是謎。"},{"pid":"d0ec1341ac1637186d5d7cf2517a1c50d6ad0d23","tid":1922944,"uid":5406,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:51:22.000Z","msg":"感染完唔諗安危<br />\n只想教波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52d8ba852b97c3560d2e2a816c1dfa49c577158","tid":1922944,"uid":160622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"好似係件大陸妹惹佢？"},{"pid":"84ee90af80fbaf4aca07c3f305c931503ba139d9","tid":1922944,"uid":330582,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d52d8ba852b97c3560d2e2a816c1dfa49c577158","tid":1922944,"uid":160622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"好似係件大陸妹惹佢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:55:14.000Z","msg":"個支那妹都幾正 都5知係味牙達完左訪問上左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7916b5eabea60f197dc9504ea26c3fffc7bc055","tid":1922944,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84ee90af80fbaf4aca07c3f305c931503ba139d9","tid":1922944,"uid":330582,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d52d8ba852b97c3560d2e2a816c1dfa49c577158","tid":1922944,"uid":160622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"